{"tha-ap189:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap189:0.2":"Kutajapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap189:0.3":"Ekacintikattheraapadana ","tha-ap189:1.1":"“Yada devo devakaya, ","tha-ap189:1.2":"cavate ayusankhaya; ","tha-ap189:1.3":"Tayo sadda niccharanti, ","tha-ap189:1.4":"devanam anumodatam. ","tha-ap189:2.1":"‘Ito bho sugatim gaccha, ","tha-ap189:2.2":"manussanam sahabyatam; ","tha-ap189:2.3":"Manussabhuto saddhamme, ","tha-ap189:2.4":"labha saddham anuttaram. ","tha-ap189:3.1":"Sa te saddha nivitthassa, ","tha-ap189:3.2":"mulajata patitthita; ","tha-ap189:3.3":"Yavajivam asamhira, ","tha-ap189:3.4":"saddhamme suppavedite. ","tha-ap189:4.1":"Kayena kusalam katva, ","tha-ap189:4.2":"vacaya kusalam bahum; ","tha-ap189:4.3":"Manasa kusalam katva, ","tha-ap189:4.4":"abyapajjam nirupadhim. ","tha-ap189:5.1":"Tato opadhikam punnam, ","tha-ap189:5.2":"katva danena tam bahum; ","tha-ap189:5.3":"Annepi macce saddhamme, ","tha-ap189:5.4":"brahmacariye nivesaya’. ","tha-ap189:6.1":"Imaya anukampaya, ","tha-ap189:6.2":"deva devam yada vidu; ","tha-ap189:6.3":"Cavantam anumodanti, ","tha-ap189:6.4":"ehi deva punappunam. ","tha-ap189:7.1":"Samvego me tada asi, ","tha-ap189:7.2":"devasanghe samagate; ","tha-ap189:7.3":"Kam su nama aham yonim, ","tha-ap189:7.4":"gamissami ito cuto. ","tha-ap189:8.1":"Mama samvegamannaya, ","tha-ap189:8.2":"samano bhavitindriyo; ","tha-ap189:8.3":"Mamuddharitukamo so, ","tha-ap189:8.4":"agacchi mama santikam. ","tha-ap189:9.1":"Sumano nama namena, ","tha-ap189:9.2":"padumuttarasavako; ","tha-ap189:9.3":"Atthadhammanusasitva, ","tha-ap189:9.4":"samvejesi mamam tada. ","tha-ap189:10.1":"Tassaham vacanam sutva, ","tha-ap189:10.2":"buddhe cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap189:10.3":"Tam dhiram abhivadetva, ","tha-ap189:10.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap189:11.1":"Upapajjim sa tattheva, ","tha-ap189:11.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap189:11.3":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap189:11.4":"duggatim nupapajjaham. ","tha-ap189:12.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap189:12.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap189:12.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap189:13.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekacintiko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap189:14.1":"Ekacintikattherassapadanam sattamam. "}